# Cloudflare Pages security headers for fluxtube.forklabs.cc.
#
# Format reference: https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/headers/
#
# Scored A+ on securityheaders.com (was A — bumped by adding `preload`
# to HSTS, the COOP/COEP/CORP cross-origin family, the
# `interest-cohort=()` opt-out, the CSP `upgrade-insecure-requests`
# directive, and tightening `form-action` to `'none'`).
#
# Identical posture to forklabs.cc — both sites are siblings under the
# same apex, and direct-to-subdomain visitors need each Pages project to
# emit its own HSTS regardless of whether the apex includeSubDomains is
# active (HSTS only kicks in after the first HTTPS visit to the domain
# that emits it). Same applies to COOP/COEP/CORP — these don't inherit
# from the apex; each subdomain has to set its own.
#
# Defaults Pages already sets (don't redeclare):
#   - x-content-type-options: nosniff
#   - referrer-policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
#   - HTTP → HTTPS 301 redirect
#
# See forklabs-cc/public/_headers for the full reasoning per directive.
# Key notes specific to this site:
#   - CSP `'unsafe-inline'` for style + script: Astro's `define:vars`
#     injects inline style attrs; the terminal type-in + countdown logic
#     ships as small inlined <script> blocks. Acceptable risk for a
#     static marketing site with zero user-controlled input.
#   - The hosted OAuth callback page (/oauth/callback) does a JS
#     window.location.search parse + writes to the DOM, all from the
#     same origin. `script-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'` covers it.
#   - COEP require-corp: Google Fonts (the only cross-origin resource
#     here) already serves CORP `cross-origin` + CORS `*`, so non-
#     breaking. Verified upstream.

/*
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains; preload
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://fonts.googleapis.com; font-src 'self' https://fonts.gstatic.com; img-src 'self' data:; script-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; connect-src 'self'; frame-ancestors 'none'; base-uri 'self'; form-action 'none'; upgrade-insecure-requests
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
  Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy: require-corp
  Cross-Origin-Resource-Policy: same-origin
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  Permissions-Policy: accelerometer=(), camera=(), geolocation=(), gyroscope=(), microphone=(), payment=(), usb=(), interest-cohort=()
